<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Xác nhận đặt vé</title>
    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Font Awesome -->
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f8ff;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 15px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff9a9e, #fad0c4);
            padding: 30px 20px;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h2 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 25px;
            color: #333333;
        }
        .ticket-info {
            background-color: #fff5f7;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .ticket-info p {
            margin: 10px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #555555;
        }
        .ticket-info strong {
            color: #ff6f61;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6f61, #ff9a9e);
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 20px 0;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(255, 111, 97, 0.2);
        }
        .button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(255, 111, 97, 0.3);
        }
        .footer {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #888888;
            padding: 15px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-ticket-alt"></i> Xác nhận đặt vé thành công!</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Xin chào <strong>{{name}}</strong>,</p>
            <p>Chúc bạn xem phim vui vẻ, nhớ đến đúng giờ nhé! Dưới đây là thông tin chi tiết về vé của bạn:</p>
            <div class="ticket-info">
                <p><strong><i class="fas fa-film"></i> Phim:</strong> {{movie}}</p>
                <p><strong><i class="fas fa-calendar-alt"></i> Ngày:</strong> {{date}}</p>
                <p><strong><i class="fas fa-clock"></i> Giờ:</strong> {{time}}</p>
                <p><strong><i class="fas fa-chair"></i> Ghế:</strong> {{seats}}</p>
                <p><strong><i class="fas fa-tag"></i> Giá vé:</strong> <span style="color: #ff6f61; font-weight: bold;">{{price}} VND</span></p>
            </div>
           
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p><i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i> Rạp chiếu phim ABC | <i class="fas fa-phone"></i> Hotline: 0123 456 789</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bootstrap JS và dependencies -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.11.6/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>